dc_description_s: These data layers represent recreational areas and water access points for Wood County, Wisconsin at year-end 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Wood_Recreation_2017.gdb'. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Wood_Recreation_Areas_2017' and 'Wood_Water_Access_2017'.
uw_supplemental_s: This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2018. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2017. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2018. This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data available, please visit: https://opendata.woodcogis.com/
